    <p>Elderberry works through different molecular pathways than the other major immune nutrients, making combinations particularly effective. The most evidence-backed adult immune stacks are:</p>

    <div class="acards">
      <a href="/immunity/best-elderberry-gummies-with-zinc-and-vitamin-c/" class="ac">
