        <h3>Elderberry + Vitamin C + Zinc</h3>
        <p>The most popular and well-supported combination. Three distinct mechanisms — viral entry blockade (elderberry), neutrophil function (vitamin C), viral replication inhibition (zinc).</p>
        <span class="ac-btn">Triple-Stack Picks &rarr;</span>
      </a>
